This program is composed of following 13 files.

main.cpp

Topping.cpp
Topping.h
ToppingList.cpp
ToppingList.h

Dough.cpp
Dough.h
DoughList.cpp
DoughList.h

Edge.cpp
Edge.h
EdgeList.cpp
EdgeList.h

Each .h file has declaration of a class, member functions and member variables with it's name. For example, Topping.h has the declartion of class Topping and its member functions and member variables in the file. 
The implementation of member functions of each class is written in cpp file with corresponding name. For example, the member functions for Topping class is implemented in Topping.cpp.
Finally, main.cpp has the main function of this program and several functions used for main function.
